name: English Garden in Gold
description:
English Garden is a lovely glass tile magnet featuring paper printed in Italy with a golden floral theme. It has a rustic and aged appearance highlighted when magnified. The glass allows each etch mark creating the flowers to be admired and appreciated. They are definitely chic and classic.

A strong neodymium magnet will hold up 6 sheets of standard paper.

These magnets are jewelry for your refrigerator or office organization!

Set of 6

7/8 inch square magnets come neatly packaged in a compact tin.

Please note: No two magnets are alike. You will receive magnets from the same paper as those pictured.

description:

These cotton folded notes have one softly deckled edge are available in five different languages (thank you, gracias, grazie, merci, and arigato).

Set includes 10 cards and envelopes. (4.25"x5.5")
